        {
            "title": "黑期低水逾400點 建行ADR績後逆市反彈",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時11分跌409點或1.64%，報24536點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股ADR指數報24705點，較香港上日現貨收市低246點或0.99%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合每股港幣487.1元，較上日香港收市低6.34元或1.29%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合每股港幣120.1元，較上日香港收市低2.47元或2.02%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合每股港幣84.6元，較上日香港收市低1.26元或1.47%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合每股港幣112.4元，較上日香港收市低1.3元或1.14%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合每股港幣32.6元，較上日香港收市低0.37元或1.12%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合每股港幣124.1元，較上日香港收市低0.74元或0.59%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合每股港幣85元，較上日香港收市低0.6元或0.7%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合每股港幣384.1元，較上日香港收市低6.35元或1.63%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合每股港幣58.4元，較上日香港收市低0.9元或1.53%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合每股港幣8.2元，較上日香港收市高0.08元或0.99%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/bplib_20230712-141204_00939_shutterstock_source-licensed_.jpg.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/bplib_20230712-141204_00939_shutterstock_source-licensed_.jpg.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指期貨夜市收報24630點，跌221點，較上日恒指收市24951點，低水322點。科指期貨夜市收報4683點，較上日科指收市低水95點；國指期貨夜市收報8340點，較上日國指收市低水114點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15810241-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4%e9%80%be400%e9%bb%9e-%e5%bb%ba%e8%a1%8cadr%e7%b8%be%e5%be%8c%e9%80%86%e5%b8%82%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%88",
